{"id": "pos037", "name": "Audio_Noah_695_06_05", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["PAFF_Sining"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "Doorbell"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Who is it?</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Sis Helena, it's been a while. This is Iris.\nWe want to talk to Aroma. Is she home right now?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>... One moment.</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Oh, Daniel, you're here as well.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Yeah, been quite some time since my last visit. Is Aroma home?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "\nHmm... Aroma can't meet with you guys now. If there's anything you want to inform her, just tell me. I'll pass it on to her.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Can't meet with us? Is she not feeling well?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "No, she is very healthy. It's just...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "That's her singing... She's practicing in her room?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Yes. Her performance is right around the corner. Therefore...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "We want to talk to her about the graduation trip. It won't take too long. After all, she's been absent from the Academy's classes recently too...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "The graduation trip? Unfortunately... I don't think Aroma will be able to participate.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "She can't even go to the graduation trip?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Yes. I also act as her agent now. I've been working with Mono to organize Aroma's schedule... I really want her to participate in the Academy's events too, but she just doesn't have any spare time left...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Then, the reason why she doesn't answer her phone these days is also...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Uh-huh. The company requested me to get her a new number. This is to avoid any inappropriate interactions or rumors before her debut... It would throw a wrench into the promotional campaign for her idol image.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Tch, all this company, idol, agent bullcrap... Aroma! You're in there, right? Show yourself!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "... Daniel! Stop that...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Right now is an important time period for Aroma. Her schedule is very tight. For her sake, please don't bother her when she's practicing.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Not even a few words?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I will tell her that you guys came. Please, just give her some more time.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "... Hmph, I'm leaving.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I'm really sorry, Iris.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "W, wait! Sis Helena!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "I would like sis Helena to tell Aroma that...\nAfter graduation... I'm moving away.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Moving away? Why all of a sudden?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Due to my father's job, we'll be living in Node 19 permanently... It's very likely that we'll never return to 08 again.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I see... what a shame.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "If possible, please tell Aroma...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "No matter what, we... will always be best friends... <i><font size=\"1.6\">*Sobs*</font></i>...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Understood. I will pass that message to her. You should go home now. It's getting late.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Yes... Thank you, sis Helena.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Don't think about it... I did the right thing.</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">I have to... protect Aroma no matter the cost...</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["PAFF_Sining"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "ドアベル"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>どなた？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helenaさん、お久しぶりです。\nIrisです。\n私たち、Aromaに会いたいんですけど、家にいますか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……ちょっと待っててもらえるかしら？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あら、Daniel君も来てたのね。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "はい。\nお久しぶりです。\nAromaはいますか？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "えっと……Aromaはあなたたちには会えないの。\n何か用事があるなら、私が伝えておくわ。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "会えないって……具合でも悪いんですか？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "いいえ、元気よ。ただ……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "あいつの歌声……部屋で歌の練習してるのか？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そうよ。\nもうすぐステージだから……その……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "卒業旅行のことについて話したくて来たんです。\nあまり時間はかかりません。\n最近はアカデミーにも来てないし……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "卒業旅行？\n残念だけど……Aromaは参加できそうにないの。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "卒業旅行にも来れないんすか？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そうよ。\n私、今はあの子のマネージャーをしてるんだけど、今スケジュールを組んでいてね……\nできるだけアカデミーの活動には参加させてあげたいのだけれど……本当に時間がないのよ……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "じゃあ、最近電話がつながらないのも……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "事務所からの要望で、電話番号を変えたの。\nメジャーデビュー前に変な噂が流れると良くないから……\nイメージを守るための戦略なのよ。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "っチ。何が事務所だよ。\n何がアイドルだよ、マネージャーだよ……\nAroma！いるんだろ？出て来いよ！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……Daniel！ダメだよ……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……今はAromaにとってとても大切な時期なの。\n時間もないわ。\nあの子のためを思うなら、練習の邪魔はしないであげて。\nお願い。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "一言二言話すのもダメなのかよ……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あなたたちが来てくれたことは、私からあの子に伝えておくわ。\nあと少し待ってちょうだい。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……ふん、俺帰るわ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ごめんなさいね、Irisちゃん。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "ま、待ってください！Helenaさん！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "どうかした？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aromaに伝えてほしいことがあるんです……\n私、卒業したら……引っ越すんです。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "引っ越し？また急ね。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "父の仕事の関係で。\nNode19に引っ越します。\n……きっともう08に帰ってくることはないと思います。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そうなの……残念だわ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "もしよければ、Aromaに伝えてください……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "何があっても、私たちは……ずっと親友だよって……<font size=\"1.6\">うう……っ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……分かったわ。\n伝えておく。\nもうこんな時間よ。\n早く帰りなさい。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "はい……ありがとうございます……Helenaさん……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "ドアを閉める"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">余計なことは考えちゃダメ……これでいいのよ。</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">私は……Aromaを守らないといけないのだから……</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["PAFF_Sining"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>哪位？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helena 姐，好久不見，我是 Iris。\n我們想找 Aroma，請問她在家嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……麻煩等我一下。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "啊，Daniel 也來了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "對啊，好久沒來打擾了。Aroma 在嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗯……Aroma 她沒辦法和妳們見面，有什麼事和我說就好。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "沒辦法見面？身體不舒服嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不不，她很健康，只是……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "那是她的歌聲……她在房間練唱？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "是啊，演出就快到了，所以……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "我們想和她談談畢業旅行的事，不會花太多時間的。畢竟她最近也不去學院上課了……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "畢業旅行嗎？可惜……我想 Aroma 應該是沒辦法參加的。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "連畢旅都不能去？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "是啊，我現在是她的經紀人，在和單聲安排 Aroma 的行程……我也很想讓她參加學院的活動，但真的抽不出空檔……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "那，最近電話都打不通也是……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗯，公司要我幫她換一支號碼，避免在正式出道前有什麼不當的交際或流言……會打亂偶像形象的宣傳戰略。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "呿，什麼公司、偶像、經紀人……Aroma！妳在的吧？出來一下！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……Daniel！別這樣……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……現在是 Aroma 最重要的時期，時間很緊迫。為了她好，請別打擾她練習，拜託了。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "只是說幾句話也不行？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我會告訴她你們來過的，再等一陣子吧。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……哼，我回去了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "抱歉了，Iris。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "等、等等！Helena 姐！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "怎麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "請 Helena 姐幫我告訴 Aroma……\n我畢業後……就要搬家了。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "搬家？怎麼這麼突然？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "爸爸工作的關係，以後我們會在 Node 19 定居……應該不會再回來 08 了。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "這樣啊……真可惜呢。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "可以的話，請幫我和 Aroma 說……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "無論如何，我們……永遠都是最好的朋友……<font size=\"1.6\">嗚嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我明白了，我會和她說的。來，時候不早了，快回去吧。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯……謝謝 Helena 姐。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">別想了……這樣做是對的。</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我一定要……好好保護 Aroma……</font>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["PAFF_Sining"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "도어벨"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>누구세요?</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helena 언니, 오랜만이에요. Iris에요.\nAroma를 만나러 왔는데, 혹시 집에 있나요?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>...잠깐 기다리렴.</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아, Daniel도 왔구나.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "네. 오랜만이에요.\nAroma는 있어요?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응... Aroma는 지금 너희들을 만나기 힘들어. 할 말 있으면 내가 전해줄 테니 내게 말하렴.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "만나기 힘들다고요? 어디 아파요?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아니, 건강해. 다만...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "저 목소리는... 방 안에서 노래 연습하고 있나봐요?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응. 공연이 곧 코앞이라... 그래서...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "졸업 여행에 관해서 같이 토론 좀 하려고 하는데, 금방 끝낼게요. 최근에 수업도 나오질 않고 그래서...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "졸업 여행? \n이런... Aroma는 아마 갈 수 없을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "졸업 여행도 못 간다고요?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응. 난 지금 그 아이의 매니저잖니. 모노와 함께 Aroma의 스케줄을 배정해야 하는데... 나도 Aroma가 그런 아카데미 활동에 참여했으면 하는 바람이지만 정말로 시간을 내기가 힘들단다...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "그럼 최근 전화가 안 된 것도...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응. 회사에서 번호를 바꾸라고 요구하더라고. 정식 데뷔 전에 루머 같은 거 나오지 않도록 하려면 그렇게 해야 한다고... 최대한 아이돌 이미지에 손상이 가지 않도록 조심하려는 마케팅 전략 같은 거라서.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "쳇, 회사고 아이돌이고 매니저고... Aroma! 안에 있어? 나와 봐!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……Daniel! 그러지 마!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...지금은 Aroma에게 가장 중요한 시기이기도 해. 시간도 얼마 안 남았고. 그러니 노래 연습을 위해서라도 너희들이 좀 이해줬으면 해.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "단 몇 마디라도 안 되나요?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "너희들이 와준 일은 전해주도록 할게.\n당분간은 좀 기다려주렴.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...흥, 나 먼저 간다.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "미안하구나, Iris.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "자, 잠깐만요! Helena 언니!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "왜 그러니?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "저기... Aroma에게 전해주세요.\n졸업하고 나면 저... 이사 간다고요.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "이사? 이렇게 갑자기?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "아버지 일 때문에 Node 19로 가게 됐어요... 아마 08로는 다시 돌아오지 못할 것 같아요.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그렇구나... 섭섭하겠다.\n"}, {"id": 35,